{
    "version": "5.0.0.1",
    "description": "Qclaw - 腾讯电脑管家出品的 AI 助手，支持微信远程操控电脑",
    "homepage": "https://qclaw.qq.com/",
    "license": {
        "identifier": "Proprietary",
        "url": "https://qclaw.qq.com/"
    },
    "innosetup": true,
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://cdn.m.qq.com/qclaw/win/5001/QClaw-Setup-latest.exe",
            "hash": "auto"
        }
    },
    "bin": "QClaw.exe",
    "shortcuts": [
        [
            "QClaw.exe",
            "Qclaw"
        ]
    ],
    "notes": [
        "Qclaw 安装成功！",
        "",
        "功能特性：",
        "  - 微信远程操控：微信扫码绑定后，可远程操控电脑文件、浏览器、邮件",
        "  - 内置国产优质大模型，支持切换自定义模型",
        "  - Skills 生态：支持 ClawHub、GitHub 等丰富生态",
        "  - 持续记忆：记住偏好和上下文，持续成长",
        "",
        "快速上手：",
        "  1. 打开 Qclaw",
        "  2. 扫码绑定微信",
        "  3. 通过微信或电脑发消息，Qclaw 帮你执行任务",
        "",
        "官网：https://qclaw.qq.com/",
        "更新：scoop update qclaw",
        "卸载：scoop uninstall qclaw"
    ],
    "checkver": {
        "url": "https://qclaw.qq.com/",
        "regex": "win/(?<ver>\\d+)/QClaw-Setup"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "architecture": {
            "64bit": {
                "url": "https://cdn.m.qq.com/qclaw/win/$matchVer/QClaw-Setup-latest.exe"
            }
        }
    }
}
